comments: Randle (NYK) slightly extends his arm and it makes marginal contact to Hart's (POR) side that does not affect his ability to defend the driving shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) and Nurkic (POR) mutually engage in marginal contact prior to separating during the off ball screen.
Fournier (NYK) reaches in and makes incidental hand on ball contact with Nurkic (POR) as he attempts to gather the ball.

Following the incidental hand on ball contact, Nurkic (POR) briefly loses control of the ball during his gather. He then regains control of the ball and takes a legal two steps prior to his shot attempt.

Replay review of the defensive foul called on McLemore (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful. Gibson (NYK) extends his left shoulder into McLemore (POR) to deliver contact during the screen.
Gibson (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position when he makes contact with Hart's (POR) body after the release that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Gibson (NYK) and Nurkic's (POR) briefly engage in marginal contact during the rebound prior to separating.
Gibson (NYK) jumps from point A to point B and he delivers contact to Winslow's (POR) body after the release that affect his ability to follow through naturally.
Randle (NYK) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
